{"tid":2350554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"許智峯遭滙豐取消信用卡　陳振英：信用卡只提供給有信用的人","createTime":"2021-01-02T12:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T16:27:49.000Z","uid":230530,"like":7,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9db8722259e1309449115d89d53b5e76eec1de37","tid":2350554,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"身在英國的前民主黨立法會議員許智峯今早（2日）在Facebook發帖指，滙豐銀行單方面、沒有通知下取消他及家人所有滙豐信用卡，原因是銀行的「商業決定」。許智峯批評滙豐有政治考慮並有侵吞結餘之嫌，敦促滙豐公開交代事件，及要求監管機構作出調查。<br />\n<br />\n金融界立法會議員陳振英表示，銀行取消許智峯的信用卡是「很正常的事」，認為銀行向客戶批出信用卡主要依據兩大原則，分別是信用評級及有否固定收入，「加上許智峯依家係逃犯，點會有信用？」<br />\n<br />\n所以特首要現金出糧？？"},{"pid":"4359cec209814b9ea4a90bc6cf13761c3fdffda4","tid":2350554,"uid":33618,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"唔怪得支国唔興信用卡"},{"pid":"4270b7f92f29c86c3c13477de645cea348b493a8","tid":2350554,"uid":66324,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"不如由金融界代表陳議員接受制裁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b931e437d8a723903cb749977e306111d0ac2f30","tid":2350554,"uid":46746,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"冇信用得過強國？"},{"pid":"23350730fc255f140cea2f918b093fc7ffb070ac","tid":2350554,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"笑支那狗？"},{"pid":"5bbdc79b73300bb1da329fb16d0595d45666afd7","tid":2350554,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"被制裁果班人信用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7703d4b7c30b89cc1d4c99af538e984f4eda9bdf","tid":2350554,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"唔怪得柒婆無得用啦"},{"pid":"5bdbb6fd8d31baf044c72d027763ba5024ce2792","tid":2350554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1